In case there was an incident, the Team also evaluated the mitigation systems like sprinkler and water deluge systems to either dilute or keep below the explosion point of a gas release; and dikes to insure that the release does not spread and contaminate the surrounding ground.





FIVE-YEAR ACCIDENT HISTORY





Formosa Plastics Corporation, Texas #3 has an excellent record of accident prevention over the past 5 years.  There has been no recordable quantity release during the past five years.  There were zero number of incidents that occurred during the past 5 years.





SUPPORT ORGANIZATIONS

Support Organizations are provided by Formosa Plastics Main site and are as follows



Administration Department



Plans, organizes, directs, and controls the activities of the administrative services to carry out the administrative support operations at the company.



Inventory Control: Total commitment to providing service by ensuring that proper material stock levels are maintained, all materials received meet specifications, and right materials of the best quality are delivered at the correct time.



Human Resources: Provides quality service to Operation Units in Human Resource management, i. e., securing consistency in the applications, policy, training, and providing timely answers to employee's questions,
